<div type="abstract"><head>Offener Brief des Rates</head><p>Der Rat bevollmächtigt Konrad Pilsacher und Hans Stetzman, Diener der Stadt, zur Vertretung vor dem Landgericht zu Hirschberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_207" id="103r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_207_r1l21">Wir ~ die <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des Rats / <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>Bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>öffenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> mit <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> brief / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l22">v̈mb ſölich ladung / vnd klag / als hans <expan>Rewt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>lantriht<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu hirſperg tut / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l23">auch getan / hintʒ allen den guten / vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> habe / die vvir die <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>gemeinl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l24">des Rats / <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> in der grafſchaft cʒu hirſperg ligend haben / vnd als <expan>dieſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l25">klag <expan>aufgeſlage<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>biſʒh<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſtande<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt / Alſo ſchicken vvir . C. <expan>Pilſach<ex>er</ex></expan> / vnd Hanſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l26">Stetʒman <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>diene<ex>r</ex></expan> / vnd geben den <expan>gantʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gevvalt / die ſache cʒu handeln </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l27">vnd das mit dem rehten cʒu <expan>verantvvurte<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd cʒe vertreten / an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtat / cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l28">gevvÿnne / vnd cʒu verluſt / vnd cʒu allen <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Mit <expan>vꝛk<ex>unde</ex></expan> <expan>At<ex>er</ex>g<ex>o</ex></expan> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> feria <expan>q<ex>ua</ex>rta</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l30">ante Erhardj / Anno . xȷ<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_207" id="103r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des rats <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        stat czu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, <expan>bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>öffenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> mit <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan> brief
                        ümb sölich ladung und klag, als Hans <expan>Rewt<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>lantriht<ex>er</ex></expan> czu Hirsperg, tut und auch getan
                        hincz allen den guten und <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> habe, die wir, die
                                <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>gemeinl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> des rats <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        stat czu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> in der grafschaft czu Hirsperg
                        ligend haben, und als <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> klag
                                <expan>aufgeslage<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>biszh<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gestande<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, also schicken wir
                                <expan>C<ex>onraden</ex></expan>
<expan>Pilsach<ex>er</ex></expan> und Hansen Steczman,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>diene<ex>r</ex></expan>, und geben den
                            <expan>gancze<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        gewalt, die sache czu handeln und das mit dem rehten czu
                                <expan>verantwurte<ex>n</ex></expan> und cze vertreten an
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat, czu gewynne und czu verlust und
                        czu allen <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Mit
                            <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan>
<expan>at<ex>er</ex>g<ex>o</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> feria
                                <expan>q<ex>ua</ex>rta</expan> ante Erhardi anno xi<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
